    "expert": "I need MedicationRequest resources for any prostate cancer hormonal therapy. Use these RxNorm ingredient codes: 42375 (leuprolide, GnRH agonist), 83008 (bicalutamide, anti-androgen), 1307298 (enzalutamide), 1100072 (abiraterone), 475230 (degarelix, GnRH antagonist). Combine in a single comma-separated code search. These drugs are essentially PCa-specific \u2014 minimal cross-indication."
